d by vampires or other monsters.\t\t\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n8\t\tA radical experiment changed your body, making you reliant on others for vital fluids.\t\t\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n\n",
